                        <li> Mritthunjaya Homam                                     </li>
                        <li> Homam of the Life                                      </li>
                        <li> Dhanvanthri Oushatha Homam                             </li>
                        <li> Sashti Homam                                           </li>
                        <li> Durga Homam                                            </li>
                        <li> Sudharshana Homam                                      </li>
                        <li> Ashta Lakshmi Homam                                    </li>
                        <li> Maha Vishnu Homam                                      </li>
                        <li> Sashtiapthapoorthi / Bheemaratha /Sadhabishega  Homam  </li>
                        <li> Homam of the Whole Family Stars                        </li>
